com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal

Class InMemoryPartitionKeyDefinitionMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.documentdb.internal.InMemoryPartitionKeyDefinitionMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PartitionKeyDefinitionMap

    public final class InMemoryPartitionKeyDefinitionMap
extends Object
implements PartitionKeyDefinitionMap
    This class implements a in-memory partition key definition cache used to extract partition key values from a document when partition key is not specified by the user in create and read document scenarios.
